The most celebrated aspirant, Alhaji Ahmed Adamu alias Sarkin Ado has today picked his All Progressives Congress (APC) Expression of Interest and Nomination forms for the 2023 election into the Yobe State House of Assembly to represent Potiskum Central Constituency. One of the strong supporters told Daily Independent that the aspirant led a team to pick the form at the APC Secretariat, Damaturu, the state capital. He is the right man for the job as he is the only aspirant in Potiskum town that is being highly celebrated by the youth and the elderly because of his philanthropic gesture to the orphans, widows and less privileged‚Äù. -Advertisement- The obtain of his nomination form threw Potiskum residents into jubilation and Celebrations.